en\">Martin Knudsen</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Friedrich_Hasen%C3%B6hrl\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Friedrich Hasenöhrl\">Friedrich Hasenöhrl</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Georges_Hostelet\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Georges Hostelet\">Georges Hostelet</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edouard_Herzen\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Edouard Herzen\">Edouard Herzen</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Hopwood_Jeans\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:James Hopwood Jeans\">James Hopwood Jeans</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernest_Rutherford\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ernest Rutherford\">Ernest Rutherford</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heike_Kamerlingh_Onnes\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Heike Kamerlingh Onnes\">Heike Kamerlingh Onnes</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Albert_Einstein\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Albert Einstein\">Albert Einstein</a>, and <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Langevin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Paul Langevin\">Paul Langevin</a>.</dd></dl>", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "DateTimeOriginal": {"value": "2 November 1911 (30.10.-03.11.1911)", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "Credit": {"value": "<bdi><a href=\"https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q33206336\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"d:Q33206336\"><span title=\"French photographer\">Benjamin Couprie</span></a></bdi>", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "Artist": {"value": "<bdi><a href=\"https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q33206336\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"d:Q33206336\"><span title=\"French photographer\">Benjamin Couprie</span></a></bdi>", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "LicenseShortName": {"value": "Public domain", "source": "commons-desc-page", "hidden": ""}, "UsageTerms": {"value": "Public domain", "source": "commons-desc-page"}, "AttributionRequired": {"value": "false", "source": "commons-desc-page", "hidden": ""}, "Copyrighted": {"value": "False", "source": "commons-desc-page", "hidden": ""}, "Restrictions": {"